=============================================================
                                                             
   A user-friendly alternative to Microsoft Access or KEXI.  
           Cross-platform and fully open source.             

----------------------[ Installation ]-----------------------

1. Make sure the git submodules are fully cloned:

   git submodule update --init --force --remote

2. Build and compile:

   autoreconf -i && ./configure && make && make execute

-------------------------------------------------------------